rows.label: qst200231_0010
rows.name: As expected, Glen.

rows.label: qst200231_0020
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]!?

rows.label: qst200231_0030
rows.name: To go this far, it's quite something.

rows.label: qst200231_0040
rows.name:
But, with this, you
understand now, right?

rows.label: qst200231_0050
rows.name: Look at it, this scene[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst200231_0060
rows.name: All of this was created by that woman.

rows.label: qst200231_0070
rows.name:
She sought money in order
to save her sick mother.

rows.label: qst200231_0080
rows.name:
The means for that was the dancing she
loved. She made what she liked into a job.

rows.label: qst200231_0090
rows.name:
In other words, she was doing the
right thing using the right means.

rows.label: qst200231_0100
rows.name: But, she was possessed by greed[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst200231_0110
rows.name:
She was charmed by a method to earn even
more money[ML:Dash ] And this is the result.

rows.label: qst200231_0120
rows.name:
The justice you believe in breaks so easily[ML:Dash ]
It just becomes fertilizer for greed.

rows.label: qst200231_0130
rows.name:
Because to stick to her own justice,
she committed such evil deeds.

rows.label: qst200231_0140
rows.name: Cut the crap, you bastard[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst200231_0150
rows.name:
Just how much do you have to mock
people before you're satisfied[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst200231_0160
rows.name:
This is all that girl's fault? There is no
justice in people? [17]: Don't screw around.

rows.label: qst200231_0170
rows.name: You are the deluded one.

rows.label: qst200231_0180
rows.name:
Something like this, it's
all your fault, isn't it!

rows.label: qst200231_0190
rows.name:
You're just manipulating people
because you want to enjoy yourself!

rows.label: qst200231_0200
rows.name:
Heh[ML:Dash ] I just gave their backs
a light push, though[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst200231_0210
rows.name: Listen up. I'm gonna beat you up now.

rows.label: qst200231_0220
rows.name: Psych yourself up and take my justice!
